item.content:encoded:
Boot Cover is made of 72 gsm Polypropylene Spunbond or Spunlace nonwoven fabric for various applications which are mainly used in industrial, agricultural and medical areas.

Specifications

  • 72 gsm, Polypropylene Spunlace nonwoven fabric
  • Free size( Suit for most of the boot )
  • Standard and with/without reinforced
  • Firmly done by sewing machine

Packing
Bag containing a pair of size 5 x 8 inches
20 bags size 5 x 8 inches per bag 14 x 20.5 inches
5 bags size 14 x 20.5 inches per carton

Available
Blue colour

item.content:encoded:
Shoe Cover is made of High Density Polyethylene to give protection from dirtand splash contamination control.
It’s ideal for guests, visting to a house or clean room manufacturing factories.

Specifications

  • High density Polyethylene ( PE )
  • Regular size and cover most shoe size
  • Firmly done with sewing machine maintaining it’s hygienic importance
  • Secure fit
  • Comply with EN 14683, CE marking, ISO 9001 and 14001

Packing
100 pcs per poly bag
20 poly bags per carton (2000pcs)

Available
Blue colour as requested
